ow][et_pb_row column_structure=\"2_3,1_3\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"INtro\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]The Golden Fleece Trading Company in Stroud, Gloucestershire is owned and run by Juliette Leighton, and trades directly with quality <a href=\"#artisans\">artisans</a> in Morocco to offer you the opportunity to experience the vibrance of colour and form that these people create.[/et_pb_text][et_pb_testimonial author=\"Juliette Leighton\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<p>My dear husband Larry Leighton, passed away on 3rd October 2019. He was suffering from Parkinson / P.S.P. Since 2014 and died at home surrounded by friends and myself.</p>\n<p>Larry accepted his illness with courage and dignity and kept his love, the sparkle in his eyes and his humour right to the end. He is helping The Golden Fleece Trading Company from the other side.</p>[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://www.goldenfleecetrading.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/21435123513_b37afed2c5_o.jpg\" alt=\"Juliette and Larry in 2006\" title_text=\"Juliette and Larry in 2006\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" _module_preset=\"default\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" admin_label=\"Section\" module_id=\"merchandise\" _builder_version=\"3.22\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" custom_padding_tablet=\"50px|0|50px|0\" custom_padding_phone=\"\" transparent_background=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" custom_padding=\"|||\" custom_padding__hover=\"|||\"][et_pb_gallery gallery_ids=\"112,113,107,100,103,116,111,101\" posts_number=\"10\" show_title_and_caption=\"off\" show_pagination=\"off\" admin_label=\"Merchandise gallery\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"][/et_pb_gallery][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" custom_padding=\"|||\" custom_padding__hover=\"|||\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://www.goldenfleecetrading.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/21868511700_87c456daa4_o.jpg\" alt=\"Goldenfleece Trading Company\" title_text=\"Goldenfleece Trading Company\" align_tablet=\"center\" align_phone=\"\" align_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" admin_label=\"Golden Fleece Interior\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" animation=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_3,2_3\" admin_label=\"Row\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" custom_padding=\"|||\" custom_padding__hover=\"|||\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"We trade in: text\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]We trade in:\n<ul>\n \t<li>Henna lamps</li>\n \t<li>Brass lanterns</li>\n \t<li>Mirrors</li>\n \t<li>Seagrass baskets and stools</li>\n \t<li>Furniture</li>\n \t<li>Leather pouffes</li>\n 