rpets</li>\r\n<li>Hand-beaten metal sinks</li>\r\n<li>Handmade mosaic tables</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nWe also sell a range of sheepskin rugs, deer and goatskins, cow hides and parchement.\r\n\r\nIn buying these items you are helping to keep alive age-old traditions, which we support in a modest way in our endeavours to develop fair-trade relationships between artisans and consumers.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Golden Fleece Trading Company\" src=\"https://www.goldenfleecetrading.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/21435711473_b822393248_k.jpg\" alt=\"Golden Fleece Trading Company\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" animation=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" title_text=\"Golden Fleece Trading Company\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_image][et_pb_image admin_label=\"Juliette and Larry Leighton\" src=\"https://www.goldenfleecetrading.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/21435123513_b37afed2c5_o.jpg\" alt=\"Juliette and Larry Leighton\" show_in_lightbox=\"off\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_overlay=\"off\" animation=\"off\" sticky=\"off\" align=\"left\" force_fullwidth=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_gallery admin_label=\"Merchandise gallery\" gallery_ids=\"112,113,107,100,103,116,111,101\" fullwidth=\"off\" posts_number=\"10\" show_title_and_caption=\"off\" show_pagination=\"off\" background_layout=\"light\" auto=\"off\" hover_overlay_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.9)\" caption_all_caps=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_gallery][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section admin_label=\"Sec