r=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]The Journeys Of a Life-Time were small  adventures organised by Larry and Juliette with the aim of going a step deeper into Moroccan life than \'normal\' tourism, tasting more of the colour, vibrance and spice that the people there emanate and resound into their environment. The aim was to give each participant the opportunity to dip \'under the skin\' of what they meet, have sufficient space to breathe this in and digest it.\n\nThe idea for the journeys originally flowered from the wish to bring together Biography work (a process of personal discovery and development) and the adventure of travel. The  journeys were tailored to particular requests and groups.[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" custom_padding=\"|||\" custom_padding__hover=\"|||\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]Juliette was born in Morocco, having left for France, with her family, in her teens. Each time she returns there she finds a renewed discovery of her people and native culture. \n\nLarry brought his intimate relationship to Morocco into this: he first got a nose for leather in Fes, before taking up working with it for a quarter of a century; for many years he has been trading directly with fine craftsmen there. [/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.6.6\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Larry shop video\" _builder_version=\"3.27.4\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" locked=\"off\"]<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hN1CYMq8VBg?rel=0\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\r[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Larry Leighton','','inherit','closed','closed','','261-revision-v1','','','2020-11-04 15:22:43','2020-11-04 15:22:43','',261,'https://www.goldenfleecetrading.co.uk/261-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
