rpets</li>\r\n<li>Hand-beaten metal sinks</li>\r\n<li>Handmade mosaic tables</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nWe also sell a range of sheepskin rugs, deer and goatskins, cow hides and parchement.\r\n\r\nIn buying these items you are helping to keep alive age-old traditions, which we support in a modest way in our endeavours to develop fair-trade relationships between artisans and consumers.\r[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" custom_padding=\"|||\" custom_padding__hover=\"|||\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://www.goldenfleecetrading.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/21435711473_b822393248_k.jpg\" alt=\"Golden Fleece Trading Company\" title_text=\"Golden Fleece Trading Company\" align_tablet=\"center\" align_phone=\"\" align_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" admin_label=\"Golden Fleece Trading Company\" _builder_version=\"3.23\" animation=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" sticky=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\"][/et_pb_image][et_pb_image src=\"https://www.goldenfleecetrading.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/21435123513_b37afed2c5_o.jpg\" alt=\"Juliette and Larry Leighton\" align_tablet=\"center\" align_phone=\"\" align_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" admin_label=\"Juliette and Larry Leighton\" _builder_version=\"3.23\" animation=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" sticky=\"off\" always_center_on_mobile=\"on\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" inner_shadow=\"on\" fullwidth=\"on\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" admin_label=\"Section\" module_class=\"divider-img\" _builder_version=\"3.22\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" background_image=\"https://www.goldenfleecetrading.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/full-width-slipper.jpg\" custom_padding_tablet=\"50px|0|50px|0\" custom_padding_phone=\"\" transparent_background=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"off\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width