=\"Row\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" custom_padding=\"|||\" custom_padding__hover=\"|||\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"INtro\" _builder_version=\"3.27.4\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]The Golden Fleece Trading Company in Stroud, Gloucestershire, is owned and run by Larry and Juliette Leighton, who trade directly with quality <a href=\"#artisans\">artisans</a> in Morocco to offer you the opportunity to experience the vibrance of colour and form that these people create.\r[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Merch text\" _builder_version=\"3.27.4\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]We trade in:\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li>Henna lamps</li>\r\n \t<li>Brass lanterns</li>\r\n \t<li>Mirrors</li>\r\n \t<li>Seagrass baskets and stools</li>\r\n \t<li>Furniture</li>\r\n \t<li>Leather pouffes</li>\r\n \t<li>Babouches and bags</li>\r\n \t<li>Silk and wool throws and cushions</li>\r\n \t<li>Safi pottery</li>\r\n \t<li>Tagines</li>\r\n<li>Carpets</li>\r\n<li>Hand-beaten metal sinks</li>\r\n<li>Handmade mosaic tables</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nWe also sell a range of sheepskin rugs, deer and goatskins, cow hides and parchement.\r\n\r\nIn buying these items you are helping to keep alive age-old traditions, which we support in a modest way in our endeavours to develop fair-trade relationships between artisans and consumers.\r[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.25\" custom_padding=\"|||\" custom_padding__hover=\"|||\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://www.goldenfleecetrading.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/21435711473_b822393248_k.jpg\" alt=\"Golden Fleece Trading Company